name: Habitat 2.0
description:
Habitat 2.0 show us one of the
possible megastructures of the future.
A residential complex in which the
individual housing units are positioned
in a chaotic way without an urban
planning, other than to concentrate as
many apartments as possible in a
megastructure . This feature reflects
the evolution of a society
characterized by frenzy and little
respect for the rights of individual
inhabitants forced to live in
increasingly anonymous spaces. The
technique used for this work is 3D
modeling
